5: Happiest of holidays to you all!
8:
What do you think of my outfit? I am
rather unused to these garments,
but I do hope they fit the occasion.
12:
It's almost like they fit... TOO well?
You look fantastic.
18: I like it a lot. You look amazing.
22:
Tee-hee! Thank you both for
flattering me!
25:
But... should it really be me handing
out all the gifts for the Guild?
30:
Heyo! We're completely on board
with it! In fact, a whole lotta
merchants who do business with
the Guild...
33:
...Made it VERY clear they wanted
you for this job, to tell ya the truth!
37:
Thanks to that, we've had a bigger
budget for holiday presents than
we've ever had in the past. Yay!
41:
Of course that's what it boils down
to... But wow, Kikuno, you sure are
popular.
46:
I'll admit to popping my head into a
party here and there.
49:
Lately, I've even been called on to
help the staff. That's how they all
know me.
52:
I'm happy to help, of course.
Gathering information is much
easier when you're the one serving
the alcohol.
57:
What kind of in—ah, right, you're
looking for that parlor...
61:
What was it called again...
Hakunroh? I remember it was lost
when Eastern and Western Yamato
merged together...
65:
That's right. But to date, I've turned
up exactly zero about it. Not a whiff.
68:
And since that Shibuya place
popped up a month ago, it's
become all folks can talk about!
72:
...There have been more shifts than
usual, as well.
76:
That's not to say I've given up on
making progress. After all, those
gentlemen just LOVE a chance for a
good business opportunity!
81:
I'm also keeping hope that Hakunroh
will emerge from one of those shifts
any day now!
86:
If the Guild hears anything about it,
you'll be the first to know, Kikuno!
90:
Tee-hee! Much obliged! Now, I
believe it's time we meet the
merchants' expectations by
matching dear Lilie's energy!
94: It's time for Santa to take the stage!
101:
Come one, come all, for some
seasonal celebration! Step up and
receive a special present from yours
truly!
105:
She's doing great. Not your typical
Santa, of course, but she seems to
be making a special connection
with the kids.
109:
She's definitely a pro at livening up a
party.
114:
Oh, hello there, Madam! Happy
holidays!
117:
This is the owner of Club Eva, one of
the establishments where I help out.
She's done so much for me!
120:
The same could be said for you! If
you joined our cast permanently,
the customers would go absolutely
wild!
123:
My humblest apologies, Madam Eva.
I still have my obligations to
Hakunroh.
126:
*sigh* Rejected again. You're like
me, more stubborn than you look.
129:
Well, what do you think? Have I
improved a little in your estimations?
133:
Hm? You say that like I didn't think
you were amazing from the start.
137:
Tee-hee. You're quite the little
charmer... You know...
140:
I'm more than happy to put in EXTRA
effort when it comes to the people
of Starview Village.
143:
...Don't be afraid to reach out any
time, Alk.
147:
Oh, I would never impose more on
you.
152:
And why not?! It's what friends are
for!
156:
L-look at the two of 'em, sidlin' up
nice 'n close. That boy's got some
nerve... That should be meee!
159:
Nnh... I feel like they're staring
daggers into me...
167:
Yeah. I've felt some threatening
looks from a few around here.
Merchants, from the look of them...
170:
You there! You with the Guild?
What's the idea behind all this?!
173:
What do you mean? The Guild
hands out presents like this every
year.
176:
Don't play dumb! There's no WAY
you were able to buy all these
presents with your usual budget.
179:
How dare those CHEATERS!
Unacceptable. This is unacceptable,
you hear me?!
186:
Those scoundrels tried to curry favor
by upping their donations in secret!
But, you know what? TWO can play
at that game!
189:
Well, if it isn't Locke and a host of
other fine merchants! It's always a
pleasure to see you gentlemen.
192:
K-Kikuno! We were... well... just
thinking we hadn't done enough to
contribute and... Here, take this!
195:
My goodness! Are you sure about all
this? Well, I am just as grateful as
can be!
198:
W-we're... not just gonna sit here
and let them win!
217:
Um... Is that... supposed to be a
sleigh?!
221:
I know I said I'd help out, but...
what've I gotten myself into here?
226:
Well... There was a battle over
donations and it kinda escalated...
231:
Tee-hee! A woman's charms can
work absolute wonders when they're
used in JUST the right ways!
235:
Joyous news, everyone! Santa has
presents for you all, thanks to the
Guild and the merchants!
238:
Let yourself be filled with blissful
holiday joy, inside and out!
244:
Well... That was certainly...
something! I'm just glad everyone
got a present...
248:
You really helped out a lot today. I
know it was something of a wild ride,
but I'm glad you stuck through it to
the end.
252:
Oh, don't mention it. Not many
chances to kick up a big fuss like
that, right?
256:
Seems like the kids absolutely loved
it, too!
262: K-Kikuno! Biiiig news! They found it!
266:
That place you've been looking for!
They found it in the depths of the
Kaleidoscope!
